{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d589c42945","title":"华北局宣传部对于处置现有纪念武训办法的意见","origin":"河北省某档案馆","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8ea5416ff4","index":0,"year":1951,"month":7,"day":2,"articleId":"d589c42945"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d5212d7a9d","type":"title","text":"华北局宣传部对于处置现有纪念武训办法的意见","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d589c42945"},{"id":"0da2cbef18","type":"subtitle","text":"中央批示","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d589c42945"},{"id":"1dfb3dcfe2","type":"paragraph","text":"可予同意。但应着重教育解释，其余可以从容处理。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d589c42945"},{"id":"d288dbd82b","type":"appellation","text":"中央宣传部：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d589c42945"},{"id":"5933f82b53","type":"paragraph","text":"河北省委向华北局提出了对现有纪念武训办法的处置意见，并向华北局请示，河北省委的意见如下：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d589c42945"},{"id":"7e170c4467","type":"subtitle","text":"\"一、关于武训学校问题：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d589c42945"},{"id":"1a04760b81","type":"paragraph","text":"1、临清武训完小改为镇立第一完小。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d589c42945"},{"id":"d78e445b83","type":"paragraph","text":"2、校内影壁墙武训像用灰涂抹。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d589c42945"},{"id":"52dbdb8d1f","type":"paragraph","text":"3、校内之小纪念塔拆除。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d589c42945"},{"id":"a0e0227099","type":"paragraph","text":"4、王少文（即王丕显）像涂抹，改为校训。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d589c42945"},{"id":"c0cd4fccd0","type":"paragraph","text":"5、反革命头子所送之匾摘下。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d589c42945"},{"id":"67ad011005","type":"paragraph","text":"6、校内石碑移动位置，暂时保存，作为历史考察材料。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d589c42945"},{"id":"68d3062311","type":"subtitle","text":"二、关于武训遗迹、及其他纪念建筑物问题：","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d589c42945"},{"id":"745856d3cd","type":"paragraph","text":"1、武训纪念林及其标记（小石柱）改为九一纪念林（九一是临清解放纪念）。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d589c42945"},{"id":"8385aa964d","type":"paragraph","text":"2、公园大厅武训石像从屋内抬出，暂时保留作为历史考察材料。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d589c42945"},{"id":"2f0edab34b","type":"paragraph","text":"3、纪念林之大石碑用石灰涂抹，写上‘九一纪念林’五字。”","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d589c42945"},{"id":"94648d9141","type":"paragraph","text":"我们原则上同意他们的意见，但同时认为考虑到武训在河北、平原两省一部分群众中的影响，作法上应该慎重。我们意见：首先对群众广泛进行教育，从思想上解决问题，然后再分别不同情况作如下处置：","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d589c42945"},{"id":"a36b3b230e","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）凡私立武训学校（如北京武训小学），在对武训及电影“武训传”讨论渐趋成熟时，由他们自己提出更名和改组，我们同意批准，仍为私立学校。凡公立的武训学校（如平原武训师范），在教职员学生思想澄清后，更改校名。（按平原武训师范已改省立堂邑师范。）","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d589c42945"},{"id":"bdda371c06","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）关于纪念武训的碑文、建筑等物，在教育群众认清武训以后，由群众自觉地拆除。石刻的像、柱、碑要拔除，画像要涂抹，武训纪念林要改名。但武训墓和墓碑，应当保留不动。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d589c42945"},{"id":"93cf4fd9a8","type":"paragraph","text":"以上意见是否妥当，请批示。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d589c42945"},{"id":"5dc4847bee","type":"paragraph","text":" 华北局宣传部1951年7月2日","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d589c42945"}],"page":{"id":"d5ac7406a4","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d589c42945","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}